{"tid":1235847,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"逸東邨22歲男子墮樓亡","createTime":"2019-06-17T09:16:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T09:17:17.000Z","uid":59227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8c48d2867cce9a52c0b2a3c4cc39086c4525a116","tid":1235847,"uid":59227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T09:16:12.000Z","msg":"點解東涌成日有人跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n東涌逸東(二)邨信逸樓發生墮樓事件。今日(16日)下午1時許，警方接獲多名市民報案，指一名男子倒臥在上址大廈對開地面，全無聲息。警方及救護員接報到場，經檢驗後證實男子已經死亡。警方經調查後，證實死者姓馮(22歲)，相信從大廈一單位墮下，現場檢獲遺書，事件無可疑，但馮的死因仍待剖驗確定。據悉，馮有情緒病紀錄，不排除因病輕生。 <br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線： <br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222 <br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000 <br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288 <br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255 <br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000 <br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281 <br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350 <br />\n利民會： 3512 2626 <br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190616/mobile/bkn-20190616173739099-0616_00822_001.html?fbclid=IwAR2X2zIPk6_eCjELmDZ3ypmdKynsMNOp0NNzhHRZ9s3spEdEHdvL_aBIcLs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190616%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190616173739099-0616_00822_001.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2X2zIPk6_eCjELmDZ3ypmdKynsMNOp0NNzhHRZ9s3spEdEHdvL_aBIcLs&d=goC%2B%2BwCxwRgX8SEPTes0u%2FdVh5kQGr0UM1CkPSjmotI%3D&h=72a00e80\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190616/mobile/bkn-20190616173739099-0616_00822_001.html?fbclid=IwAR2X2zIPk6_eCjELmDZ3ypmdKynsMNOp0NNzhHRZ9s3spEdEHdvL_aBIcLs</a>"},{"pid":"eaeff883b2045ced3d079aba26a65fb16d39090b","tid":1235847,"uid":24180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T09:17:17.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}